### 수강 신청 (201 Created, 초기 상태 PENDING)
POST http://localhost:8080/courses/1/enrollments
X-User-Id: 100

### 결제 확정 (200 OK, PENDING → CONFIRMED, 소유자만)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/enrollments/1/confirm
X-User-Id: 100

### 수강 취소 (200 OK, PENDING/CONFIRMED → CANCELLED, 소유자만)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/enrollments/1/cancel
X-User-Id: 100

### 내 신청 목록 (200 OK, CANCELLED 포함 최신순, courseTitle 포함)
GET http://localhost:8080/enrollments/me
X-User-Id: 100
